{"word":"ἀναστέλλω","slug":"ἀναστέλλω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀναστέλλω</b></el> <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to raise up</i>:— <a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a> <i>to gird up</i> one's clothes, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to keep back, repulse</i> an attack, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to retire</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}